metadata.name: Day class implements
metadata.description:
When Huang Fan and the rest of the Huang family heard this, they fell into an ice cave.



The crimson is gone, and the hot sun is high overhead.



The Huangs, however, felt as if they were in a frozen world.



A great sense of humiliation, brewing in the heart of Huang Fan, let him a few to collapse.



His yellow family, for the blood god religion, has exhausted everything!
